      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone looking for affordable transportation or a practical project. It presents honestly, starts up, and offers a cost-effective entry point into ownership without the premium price tag. A sensible choice for buyers who prioritize price, utility, and opportunity.",
