      "description": "If you\u2019re after a cheap set of wheels and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this car could be a great fit. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option with plenty of potential for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone needing a simple runaround. Priced fairly for what it is, and a nice chance to get on the road without spending a fortune.",
